-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.2k</span></span></a> — a toolbelt plugin that adds extra useful plugins for working with Postgres. Things like analyzing cache hit rates, outlier queries, unused indexes, table sizes, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"img-width21-height21-srchttpsgithubcomianstormtaylorawesome-herokurawmasterimagesgoodbyepng-goodbye\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#img-width21-height21-srchttpsgithubcomianstormtaylorawesome-herokurawmasterimagesgoodbyepng-goodbye\" aria-label=\"img width21 height21 srchttpsgithubcomianstormtaylorawesome herokurawmasterimagesgoodbyepng goodbye permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img width=\"21\" height=\"21\" src=\"https://github.com/ianstormtaylor/awesome-heroku/raw/master/images/goodbye.png\"> Goodbye...</h2>\n<p>Things to check out if you decide to migrate off of Heroku for some reason...</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tool</code> <a href=\"http://dokku.viewdocs.io/dokku/\">dokku</a> — a self-hosted, docker-based, Heroku-compliant platform.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"img-width21-height21-srchttpsgithubcomianstormtaylorawesome-herokurawmasterimageslicensepng-license\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#img-width21-height21-srchttpsgithubcomianstormtaylorawesome-herokurawmasterimageslicensepng-license\" aria-label=\"img width21 height21 srchttpsgithubcomianstormtaylorawesome herokurawmasterimages